summary: Well this is a first.
title: Well this is a first.
body:
So yesterday I told my gf in the car that I bought a burrito at school cause I haven’t eaten the whole day and I told the cashier that I want to get a Tex-mex burrito cause I haven’t gone there and that one seemed reasonable. So I placed my order.
Then the cashier asked “Would you like some protein with that?” and I’m like “what?!”
And then she repeated the question. And I’m still like what about protein lady?
She eventually said “would you like some chicken, steak, etc..”
I’m like “oh ok…steak pls….”
Upon hearing all of this my gf immediately went and said “PROTEEEINNNN!!” out loud and I just lost it.

Ps. I want more aggretsuko.

summary: ☆☆ GUEST ANNOUNCEMENT - ERICA MENDEZ ☆☆ https://kamicons11.eventbrite.com - Book Now for $10 Off! Singing angrily in the...
caption:
☆☆ GUEST ANNOUNCEMENT - ERICA MENDEZ ☆☆
https://kamicons11.eventbrite.com - Book Now for $10 Off!

Singing angrily in the Kami-Con karaoke room, we’ve got… ERICA MENDEZ!

Erica was born and raised in the suburbs of Chicago. She became interested in voice-over during her early teen years through animation and video games. Making up and imitating voices from her favorite shows and games as a hobby quickly turned into long term goal to get into the voice-over industry. Several years and one giant move across the country later, she is currently residing in Los Angeles and working as a professional voice-over artist.

Her very first role in major studio project was the iconic character, Pac-Man, in the “Pac-Man and the Ghostly Adventures” video game. Soon after that, she was cast in a multitude of roles! Such as:

- Retsuko (Aggrestuko)
- Ryuko Matoi (Kill la Kill)
- Nico Yazawa (Love Live!)
- Akko Kagari (Little Witch Academia)
- Gon (Hunter X Hunter)
- Sailor Uranus/Amara (Sailor Moon)
- Yuuki Konno (Sword Art Online II)
- Diane (The Seven Deadly Sins)
- Aladdin (Magi)
- Mash Kyrielight (Fate/Grand Order)
- Puck (Re:Zero)
- Chiriko “Tsuruko” Tsurumi (Anohana)
- Kenya Kobayashi (Erased)
- Assassin of Black/Jack the Ripper (Fate/Apocrypha)
- Seong Mi-na (Soul Calibur VI)
- Pac-Man (Pac-Man and the Ghostly Adventures 1-2)

She’ll be at Kami-Con hosting panels, taking photos, signing autographs, and more, so come and see her!

http://www.kamicon.net
